The evidence with the title 'Walker taking gas tax argument to voters at the pumps ' says Oct 9, 2018  ... Gov. Scott Walker is taking his argument against raising the gas tax straight to voters at the pump .  ... Walker says in the ad it 's a "good thing you're filling up because if Tony Evers wins he 'll raise the gas tax by as much as a dollar a gallon. " Evers hasn't said how much he would be willing to raise the gas tax. 
